simple gui for drawing on an 8x8 Led array

intended for use on a RaspBerry pi with a 
Adafruit Mini 8x8 LED Matrix w/I2C hookedup

uses pygame to draw the GUI and handle click events
uses AdaFruit Libraries for setting pixels on the LED
uses json for reading/writing to a file

needs to be run with sudo to access the GPIO ie.
sudo python ledgame.py